## Next Steps

Once deployed to Vercel:
- Speed Insights will automatically begin collecting performance data
- Metrics will be available in the Vercel dashboard under the "Speed Insights" tab
- No additional configuration is required

## Notes

- The implementation follows Vercel's official documentation for Next.js 13.5+ with App Router
- No environment variables or additional configuration needed
- The component is lightweight and has no impact on bundle size for users who don't visit the Vercel dashboard
